 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of 
     the projective process of three dimensional geometry into a two dimensional space by means of
     a camera model and for the specification of lighting and clipping of the three dimensional geometry.
   </p>
 </purpose>

